module REQ_COHORT_LEADERBOARD_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-COHORT-LEADERBOARD-01
 * Title       : Cohort Leaderboard Ranked by Nuggets
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
